School does that to the best of us, yes.

::Firearm/Kluster/Prowl::

Firearm runs toward Arcangel as he sees the Maximal go into stasis lock. He 
grabs him, throwing him over his shoulder and running back toward the CF.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Kluster and Prowl run out of the CF, passing Firearm, and firing their guns 
rapidly at Dark Lord.
